
handcache use ActiveSupport::Cache::MemCacheStore to provide get_and_set method and compressed feature.

== USAGE

Add below line to your environment.rb

CacheStore = ActiveSupport::Cache::MemCacheStore.new("localhost")

Then in your code:

data = Handcache.get_and_set("data-123", :expires_in => 60 ) do
          "cached-foobar"
       end